{"tid":842844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誤傳「收禮清單」到百人群組 廣東醫師遭停職處分","createTime":"2018-09-30T15:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T22:35:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2db20b2c5f96f97465981413a3ee8599214c23","tid":842844,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpuHsKYR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpuHsKYR.jpg&h=e6c84fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國廣東一名醫生誤傳一份「中秋收禮明細」到微信的工作群組，群組內有超過100人，醜事就這麼爆開，30日已遭醫院停職、記過處分。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，中國廣東汕頭市中心醫院證實，黃姓醫師原本要傳工作紀錄照到群組，卻錯傳成他的「收賄清單」，上頭詳記了送禮人姓名、送禮品項，包括香菸、海參、雪茄、月餅等。送禮人數估計超過30人，而收到的禮物總價值逾10萬人民幣（約台幣45萬元）。工作群組內總共有119人，雖然黃姓醫師發現錯誤後馬上群組想要掩蓋，卻來不及，同事們馬上截圖存檔。<br />\n<br />\n黃姓醫師任職的醫院30日發聲明表示，已暫停該明醫師職務、記過處分，醫師部分未退回的禮金將會上繳醫院。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpKxHilF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpKxHilF.jpg&h=d3ca3d85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2566608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2566608&d=4ehNFi2R%2FwCFrCvLfGYmR57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=6a469dbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2566608&h=764b8061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2566608</a>"},{"pid":"fa6a4ab173b00e166fea0cb451f925940318348e","tid":842844,"uid":10438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T21:31:47.000Z","msg":"睇到收禮諗起第二樣野"},{"pid":"d0f2599df7a77b546c7d0e802b24e124feb303da","tid":842844,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T21:43:18.000Z","msg":"宋生開心死"},{"pid":"d58a4389fedc38e83e524ef2d5cb97d6c3957347","tid":842844,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T22:35:36.000Z","msg":"大陸土醫收錢就梗架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}